high_descs: Turn right and walk until you get past the sink on your left and then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the spatula.
Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the stove.
Put the spatula in the right pan.
Pick up the pan with the spatula in it.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the middle of the green table on your left and then turn left and walk to it.
Put the pan near the left edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a spatula in it on the table.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up a spatula from the counter
Move to the stove to the right of the sink
Place the spatula in the pot on the stove
Pick up the pot with a spatula from the stove
Move to the island across from the sink
Place the pot on the island.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spatula on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk across the kitchen to the counter immediately on the right of the sink.
Pick up the spatula on the right of the sink.
Move to the stove to your right.
Place the spatula inside of the pot on the right of the stove.
Pick up that same pot which now has the spatula inside.
Carry the pot with the spatula in it to the table behind you.
Place that pot with the spatula in it on the left end of the table closest to the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a spatula in it on the table.
